column3: “Beautiful strain, I feel like I'm floating on a cloud when I smoke this. I took one hit and was coughing for 10 minutes. This shit is fire”
“I love the way it looks very clean! Smells sweet and earthy and slinky. very nurturing strain it's also a hard hitter”
“Perfect mix of euphoria and spacey. Great for mornings and free time chill sessions. I tended to space out more on this so I didn't really want to use it at work lol”
“Loved it. It was good for pain relief after my back surgery. Interesting taste and earthy smells”
“When I get a hit of it. The berry flavor just goes off. Delicious!”
“amzing taste very uplifting . great for stress and feel happy after smojing this strian.”
“Great strain! Absolutely fantastic head high. The world seems brighter after the first hit.”
“Some great stuff this the stuff you smoke and feel lazy  lost in space and good”
“good color and crystals. smoked well and it was mellow but not groggy”
“Great weed, super, yet active chill mood!”
“Hey nice strain. Not quite couch lock but it hits all the right spots. Helps my pain tremendously. And I will find out in the morning how I sleep on it. Just got some tonight 😋”
